original:
This Digimon takes on the appearance of a small
chick. Though it's still physically weak and unable to
hold its own in a fight, it's still an In-Training level
Digimon and so it is easy to predict what it will
Digivolve into.
translation:
This Digimon takes on the appearance of a small
chick. Though it's still physically weak and unable to
hold its own in a fight, it's still an In-Training level
Digimon and so it is easy to predict what it will
Digivolve into.

original:
Just like other Dragon Digimon, despite its small
stature, it's full of energy. It's body has become
larger, and its fine, downy hair has fallen out.
translation:
Just like other Dragon Digimon, despite its small
stature, it's full of energy. It's body has become
larger, and its fine, downy hair has fallen out.

original:
This small Digimon is covered in a coat of flowing long
hair and possesses a tough horn atop its head. It is
quite mischievous, but isn't suited for battle yet.
translation:
This small Digimon is covered in a coat of flowing long
hair and possesses a tough horn atop its head. It is
quite mischievous, but isn't suited for battle yet.

original:
This Digimon's body is completely translucent, and it
drifts about the Net Ocean like a jellyfish. Scholars 
studying Digimon consider it the 'Missing Link', the 
key to solving the mystery of the origin of Digimon.
translation:
This Digimon's body is completely translucent, and it
drifts about the Net Ocean like a jellyfish. Scholars 
studying Digimon consider it the 'Missing Link', the 
key to solving the mystery of the origin of Digimon.

original:
This tiny Digimon has grown limb-like protrusions from
its lower body, which is quite a rare occurrence for
In-training level Digimon. It's round, chubby body is
considered very cute.
translation:
This tiny Digimon has grown limb-like protrusions from
its lower body, which is quite a rare occurrence for
In-training level Digimon. It's round, chubby body is
considered very cute.

original:
This small Digimon with leaves sprouting from its head
possesses a timid personality and dislikes fighting.
When it senses danger, it will bury itself in the dirt to
hide using its clawed feet.
translation:
This small Digimon with leaves sprouting from its head
possesses a timid personality and dislikes fighting.
When it senses danger, it will bury itself in the dirt to
hide using its clawed feet.

original:
This is a Digimon that loves mischief, as expected of
an In-Training level Digimon part of the Virus
category. It has a cynical personality, and its large
hand-like ears can even be used to fly.
translation:
This is a Digimon that loves mischief, as expected of
an In-Training level Digimon part of the Virus
category. It has a cynical personality, and its large
hand-like ears can even be used to fly.

original:
This small Digimon wears a metal helmet on its head,
which gives it superior defensive capabilities in
comparison to other In-Training Digimon. It is a
bat-like Digimon that is able to maneuver even in
pitch darkness by using sonar waves.
translation:
This small Digimon wears a metal helmet on its head,
which gives it superior defensive capabilities in
comparison to other In-Training Digimon. It is a
bat-like Digimon that is able to maneuver even in
pitch darkness by using sonar waves.

original:
This mysterious Digimon suddenly appeared on the
Computer Network and is said to have been born from
an egg filled with humanity's malice. It is able to
multiply like a virus and will destroy any network it
comes across.
translation:
This mysterious Digimon suddenly appeared on the
Computer Network and is said to have been born from
an egg filled with humanity's malice. It is able to
multiply like a virus and will destroy any network it
comes across.

original:
Because this Digimon is rumored to bring happiness,
it is an extremely popular choice amongst Tamers.
Despite its cute exterior, it had a mischievous side,
though Tamers say that's part of its charm.
translation:
Because this Digimon is rumored to bring happiness,
it is an extremely popular choice amongst Tamers.
Despite its cute exterior, it had a mischievous side,
though Tamers say that's part of its charm.

original:
While this Digimon is small and weak, it has the
potential to Digivolve into a variety of different
Dragon Digimon. Because of this, it is considered
extremely valuable by researchers and Tamers.
translation:
While this Digimon is small and weak, it has the
potential to Digivolve into a variety of different
Dragon Digimon. Because of this, it is considered
extremely valuable by researchers and Tamers.

original:
This Digimon possesses a reckless personality, and
will stand up against any threat despite its small
size. While this causes it to be difficult to tame,
it is a preferred choice by Tamers who pride
themselves in battle.
translation:
This Digimon possesses a reckless personality, and
will stand up against any threat despite its small
size. While this causes it to be difficult to tame,
it is a preferred choice by Tamers who pride
themselves in battle.

original:
This Digimon is the embodiment of the power of
Digivolution, and because of that, it is often
referred to as the 'Digi-Entelechy'. Due to this
reputation, it is said to have the power to help other
Digimon Digivolve.
translation:
This Digimon is the embodiment of the power of
Digivolution, and because of that, it is often
referred to as the 'Digi-Entelechy'. Due to this
reputation, it is said to have the power to help other
Digimon Digivolve.

original:
Though small in side, this In-Training Dragon Digimon
possesses legs, a tail, and even small wings on its
head. It has an aggressive personality, and as such,
Tamers are advised to handle it with caution.
translation:
Though small in side, this In-Training Dragon Digimon
possesses legs, a tail, and even small wings on its
head. It has an aggressive personality, and as such,
Tamers are advised to handle it with caution.

original:
This Digimon is extremely active, but is still able to
get along well with its more timid Twin, Kokomon.
The pair are always seen together, and while they
may look very similar, Gummymon is green and has
only a single horn atop its head.
translation:
This Digimon is extremely active, but is still able to
get along well with its more timid Twin, Kokomon.
The pair are always seen together, and while they
may look very similar, Gummymon is green and has
only a single horn atop its head.

original:
This rough Digimon has the destructive ability to not
only ruin data, but entire networks with incredible
speed. Due to its superior speed, it is extremely
difficult to catch, and its single eye radiates an
eerie light.
translation:
This rough Digimon has the destructive ability to not
only ruin data, but entire networks with incredible
speed. Due to its superior speed, it is extremely
difficult to catch, and its single eye radiates an
eerie light.

original:
This Digimon has a quiet personality, and wears a
tough shell made from straw to protect itself. It
travels by hanging onto bigger Digimon using the
vines that protrude from its head.
translation:
This Digimon has a quiet personality, and wears a
tough shell made from straw to protect itself. It
travels by hanging onto bigger Digimon using the
vines that protrude from its head.

original:
This Digimon's speed is its strong point, and because
of that, Tamers must be sure not to let it run off
recklessly. It was created by fusing the data of
commonly kept pets such as cats and dogs, and
because of this, it becomes attached to any Tamer
that treats it well.
translation:
This Digimon's speed is its strong point, and because
of that, Tamers must be sure not to let it run off
recklessly. It was created by fusing the data of
commonly kept pets such as cats and dogs, and
because of this, it becomes attached to any Tamer
that treats it well.

original:
This Digimon has the appearance of a flower bud,
as it was created by fusing the data of several
poisonous plants. It peacefully floats around, riding
the wind using a leaf, and while it won't initiate an
attack, it will defend itself with its sharp thorns.
translation:
This Digimon has the appearance of a flower bud,
as it was created by fusing the data of several
poisonous plants. It peacefully floats around, riding
the wind using a leaf, and while it won't initiate an
attack, it will defend itself with its sharp thorns.

original:
This newly-born Digimon is covered in black
velvet-like hairs and its body is extremely soft.
translation:
This newly-born Digimon is covered in black
velvet-like hairs and its body is extremely soft.

original:
This Digimon's form imitates the sun, and a gentle
flame flickers atop its head. It tends to float around
in the air, and possesses a happy-go-lucky
personality.
translation:
This Digimon's form imitates the sun, and a gentle
flame flickers atop its head. It tends to float around
in the air, and possesses a happy-go-lucky
personality.

original:
This Digimon has a translucent body shaped like a
water droplet with cute flushed cheeks. It possesses
a pure heart, and because of this, it is easily
affected by the personality of its Tamer.
translation:
This Digimon has a translucent body shaped like a
water droplet with cute flushed cheeks. It possesses
a pure heart, and because of this, it is easily
affected by the personality of its Tamer.

original:
Despite its small size, this purple dragon Digimon
loves to fight. It's full of energy, and will stand up to
any enemy regardless of strength, attacking fiercely
with sharp claws. It is often heard shouting
declarations of battle at anyone that annoys it.
translation:
Despite its small size, this purple dragon Digimon
loves to fight. It's full of energy, and will stand up to
any enemy regardless of strength, attacking fiercely
with sharp claws. It is often heard shouting
declarations of battle at anyone that annoys it.

original:
This reptilian Digimon has developed the ability to
walk on two legs. It has a stubborn personality and
will stand up against any enemy, using its sharp
claws and fiery 'Pepper Breath' shot from its mouth.
translation:
This reptilian Digimon has developed the ability to
walk on two legs. It has a stubborn personality and
will stand up against any enemy, using its sharp
claws and fiery 'Pepper Breath' shot from its mouth.

original:
This Digimon is thought to have descended from a
species that flourishes during the time of the Digital
World's creation. It is an energetic Digimon with a
pure heart, and the ability to 'Armor Digivolve' using
the power of a 'Digi-Egg'.
translation:
This Digimon is thought to have descended from a
species that flourishes during the time of the Digital
World's creation. It is an energetic Digimon with a
pure heart, and the ability to 'Armor Digivolve' using
the power of a 'Digi-Egg'.

original:
This Rookie Digimon is part of the Dragon family and 
has the potential to become a 'Combat Species' in the 
future. It has the 'Digital Hazard' label, indicating its 
potential to cause significant damage to data.
However, if used for peace, its untapped power
could become a tool for protecting the world.
translation:
This Rookie Digimon is part of the Dragon family and 
has the potential to become a 'Combat Species' in the 
future. It has the 'Digital Hazard' label, indicating its 
potential to cause significant damage to data.
However, if used for peace, its untapped power
could become a tool for protecting the world.

original:
Due to the outdated 'Interface' located on its
forehead, many believe that this Digimon was an
experimental 'Prototype'. It possesses a high combat
instinct, and it feels an instant sense of attachment
to whatever it bites. This mysterious Digimon has the
potential to grow into something incredible.
translation:
Due to the outdated 'Interface' located on its
forehead, many believe that this Digimon was an
experimental 'Prototype'. It possesses a high combat
instinct, and it feels an instant sense of attachment
to whatever it bites. This mysterious Digimon has the
potential to grow into something incredible.

original:
This Amphibian Digimon walks around on four legs,
and though its personality is quite timid, if it is
angered, it will lash out with an electrical shock.
translation:
This Amphibian Digimon walks around on four legs,
and though its personality is quite timid, if it is
angered, it will lash out with an electrical shock.

original:
This shy Digimon wears a fur coat made from
leftover Data from Garurumon in order to protect
itself. Though it is generally quite timid, wearing its
fur coat helps it become bold and tough.
translation:
This shy Digimon wears a fur coat made from
leftover Data from Garurumon in order to protect
itself. Though it is generally quite timid, wearing its
fur coat helps it become bold and tough.

original:
This Mammal Digimon possesses particularly large
ears that look more like wings, and while it is able to
use them to fly, it can only travel at 1km/h, thus it is
faster for it to just walk. It has the mysterious
ability to 'Armor Digivolve' using the power of a
'Digi-Egg'.
translation:
This Mammal Digimon possesses particularly large
ears that look more like wings, and while it is able to
use them to fly, it can only travel at 1km/h, thus it is
faster for it to just walk. It has the mysterious
ability to 'Armor Digivolve' using the power of a
'Digi-Egg'.

original:
This chick-like Digimon's wings have evolved into
arms, which while it can use them to fly, it is no
better than Patamon. Due to this, it tends to live on
the land, only flying when it senses danger. It dreams
of flying in the wide open sky one day.
translation:
This chick-like Digimon's wings have evolved into
arms, which while it can use them to fly, it is no
better than Patamon. Due to this, it tends to live on
the land, only flying when it senses danger. It dreams
of flying in the wide open sky one day.

original:
This Digimon has a large tropical flower growing from
its head, it's said that this flower changes its
fragrance depending on its mood. When in a good
mood, the flower will emit a pleasant sweet smell,
but when angry, it emits an intense odor that causes
even bigger Digimon to flee.
translation:
This Digimon has a large tropical flower growing from
its head, it's said that this flower changes its
fragrance depending on its mood. When in a good
mood, the flower will emit a pleasant sweet smell,
but when angry, it emits an intense odor that causes
even bigger Digimon to flee.

original:
This original type of Insect Digimon possesses a hard
shell and long sharp claws. It loves nature and has a
very carefree personality, and while many Insect
Digimon tend to be aggressive, this Digimon is quite
kind.
translation:
This original type of Insect Digimon possesses a hard
shell and long sharp claws. It loves nature and has a
very carefree personality, and while many Insect
Digimon tend to be aggressive, this Digimon is quite
kind.

original:
This Digimon covers itself in mineral data in order to
fortify its defences. The type of mineral data varies
depending on the location and condition of where it is
obtained.
translation:
This Digimon covers itself in mineral data in order to
fortify its defences. The type of mineral data varies
depending on the location and condition of where it is
obtained.

original:
This seal-like Digimon has evolved the ability to live
on the land as well as in the ocean. Its entire body is
covered in thick warm fur that continues to grow
throughout its lifetime. As it grows older, the fur
changes color from pure white to brown.
translation:
This seal-like Digimon has evolved the ability to live
on the land as well as in the ocean. Its entire body is
covered in thick warm fur that continues to grow
throughout its lifetime. As it grows older, the fur
changes color from pure white to brown.

original:
This small bat-like Digimon is said to have been the
one to tempt the originally Angel type Devimon down
the path of evil. This Digimon is crafty and wherever
it goes, bad luck is sure to follow. It dislikes direct
battle, and prefers to hide in the background and
attack from a safe distance.
translation:
This small bat-like Digimon is said to have been the
one to tempt the originally Angel type Devimon down
the path of evil. This Digimon is crafty and wherever
it goes, bad luck is sure to follow. It dislikes direct
battle, and prefers to hide in the background and
attack from a safe distance.

original:
A Digimon that was originally created by a child trying
to re-created Agumon, it possesses a keen sense of
justice, despite its timid personality. It tends to fall
to pieces when startled, and loves communicating
with children through the internet.
translation:
A Digimon that was originally created by a child trying
to re-created Agumon, it possesses a keen sense of
justice, despite its timid personality. It tends to fall
to pieces when startled, and loves communicating
with children through the internet.

original:
This gear-shaped Digimon's body is crammed full of
gears, and if even just one gets jammed, it will cease
to function. It is able to send a virus into other
Digimon's bodies with a Black Gear and control them.
translation:
This gear-shaped Digimon's body is crammed full of
gears, and if even just one gets jammed, it will cease
to function. It is able to send a virus into other
Digimon's bodies with a Black Gear and control them.

original:
This Digimon was created by a Digimon researcher as
an experiment. Though it is a Holy Digimon, it has yet
to awaken to its mission as a 'Virus Buster', and
because of this, depending on how it is raised, it
could become good or evil.
translation:
This Digimon was created by a Digimon researcher as
an experiment. Though it is a Holy Digimon, it has yet
to awaken to its mission as a 'Virus Buster', and
because of this, depending on how it is raised, it
could become good or evil.

original:
This small larval Digimon is incredibly kind hearted,
and while it's unable to match up against bigger
Digimon, once it 'Armor Digivolves', it gains access to
incredible power.
translation:
This small larval Digimon is incredibly kind hearted,
and while it's unable to match up against bigger
Digimon, once it 'Armor Digivolves', it gains access to
incredible power.

original:
This bird Digimon possesses proper manners and is
always polite to others. Due to being a descendant
of an ancient species, it has the ability to 'Armor
Digivolve' using the power of a 'Digi-Egg'.
translation:
This bird Digimon possesses proper manners and is
always polite to others. Due to being a descendant
of an ancient species, it has the ability to 'Armor
Digivolve' using the power of a 'Digi-Egg'.

original:
This Mammal Digimon wears a tough shell to protect
itself from attacks. Due to being a descendant of an
ancient species, it has the ability to 'Armor Digivolve'
using the power of a 'Digi-Egg'.
translation:
This Mammal Digimon wears a tough shell to protect
itself from attacks. Due to being a descendant of an
ancient species, it has the ability to 'Armor Digivolve'
using the power of a 'Digi-Egg'.

original:
Part of a pair of twin Digimon, this Digimon has only a
single horn on its head. While its personality isn't the
most intimidating, once it is engaged in battle, it
shows incredible power.
translation:
Part of a pair of twin Digimon, this Digimon has only a
single horn on its head. While its personality isn't the
most intimidating, once it is engaged in battle, it
shows incredible power.

original:
Part of a pair of twin Digimon, this Digimon has three
horns atop its head. Its personality is the complete
opposite of Terriermon, being more of a needy
crybaby. Despite this, when push comes to shove,
just like Terriermon, it shows incredible power.
translation:
Part of a pair of twin Digimon, this Digimon has three
horns atop its head. Its personality is the complete
opposite of Terriermon, being more of a needy
crybaby. Despite this, when push comes to shove,
just like Terriermon, it shows incredible power.

original:
This Digimon possesses incredible potential if its
ability is properly cultivated by a skilled Tamer from
the In-Training level. It relies much more on speed
than power during battle.
translation:
This Digimon possesses incredible potential if its
ability is properly cultivated by a skilled Tamer from
the In-Training level. It relies much more on speed
than power during battle.

original:
This child-like Digimon is seen as a troublesome devil
child, as it loves to play pranks and cause mischief.
It will never back down to a stronger opponent due to
its prideful personality and distaste towards losing.
Despite this, truth be told, it has a lonely side to it.
translation:
This child-like Digimon is seen as a troublesome devil
child, as it loves to play pranks and cause mischief.
It will never back down to a stronger opponent due to
its prideful personality and distaste towards losing.
Despite this, truth be told, it has a lonely side to it.
